transcript:
Customer: Hello

Executive: Hello

Customer: Haan ji.

Customer: Sir, isme IndiaMART aapke is package mein jo leads hain wo yearly to bilkul hi nahi mil rahi hai. Abhi package humne renewal karaya hai.

Executive: Sir, aapki company ka naam bata sakte hain aap?

Customer: Fresh Gene Genetics.

Executive: Fresh Gene Genetics.

Executive: Kya puch rahe hain aap? Leads ka puch rahe hain aap?

Customer: Haan haan, maximum hume kitna milta hai ye?

Executive: 44 leads milti hain aapko.

Customer: Nahi, daily ki two aa rahi hain, weekly ki 30 aa rahi hain bas.

Executive: To sir 44 ho to gayi, 7 duni 14 aur weekly 30, 44.

Customer: Nahi, 40 yearly to nahi hai na? Yearly pichli saal humne jab karaya tha do saal pehle to yearly

Executive: Yearly yearly yearly yearly zero hain sir is time pe. Yearly nahi milti hain. Yearly service ke time pe jo hoti hai.

Customer: Yearly kitne saal mili jo humne is saal baat bhi ki thi. Unhone kaha milenge.

Executive: Nahi nahi sir, main keh raha hu ki pichle saal package mein kya kariye na check karke mili ki nahi mili.

Executive: Main bilkul check kar leta hu aapka account bhi ek minute.











Executive: Ek ek minute.

Executive: Yearly buylead aapke balance mein nahi hai. Itna kar sakte hain ki hum aapko thoda sa balance yearly buylead ka na allowance kara de raha hu main, theek hai aapko?

Customer: Karwa dijiye sir. Pehle baat hui thi meri sabhi ne maximizer karwaya tha. Teen saal se karwaya hai abhi nahi mil rahi hai.

Executive: Bilkul, main aapka jo lead ka hai aap yearly bata rahe hain. Jo balance mein hongi hamare accounts ke paas wo hum aapko yearly is baar baat karke main karwa deta hu, theek hai?

Customer: Theek hai sir, kab tak ho jayengi ye?

Executive: Ye kal tak hi ho payegi sir. Agar aapne mujhe first half se pehle call kiya hota to main aapko ye clear karwa deta. But ye aapko kal dopahar tak aapko mil jayengi.

Customer: Theek hai sir, theek hai. Aap apne number se call kariye mujhe. Aap hi dekh rahe hain kya mera handle account bhi?

Executive: Account to main hi dekh raha hu.

Customer: Kya naam hai aapka?

Executive: Parvez Hashmi.

Customer: Ah, achcha achcha. Pehle aap hi dekh rahe the ki dusra dekh raha tha ki naya koi aaya?

Executive: Nahi nahi, pehle bhi main hi dekh raha tha account aapka.

Customer: Aap hi ne to karwaya tha mera ye?

Executive: Haan haan, main hi karwaya tha sir. Aap bhool kaise sakte hain ki maine nahi karwaya tha.

Customer: Nahi ispe humne wo aapka number nahi tha na mere paas to humne direct call kiya.

Executive: Koi nahi koi nahi, aapko na main ye karwa de raha hu ek baar baat karke. Jo bhi aapke jitna hamare balance mein honge us hisab se yearly yearly account mein main dal de raha hu aapke.

Customer: Nahi hai.

Customer: Theek theek theek.

Executive: Theek hai.

Executive: Okay.

Executive: Baki iske alawa
summary:
Concerns:

- Yearly leads not reflecting in account.

- Wants yearly leads as promised during renewal.



Resolution:

- Executive checked the account and confirmed no yearly buyleads.

- Promised to provide an allowance for yearly buyleads.

- Will check with accounts and add yearly leads.



Next Steps: 

- Customer will receive yearly leads by tomorrow afternoon.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Annoyed -> Satisfied



@@@Key Topics:

- buyleads, subscription, yearly leads, account balance
